high_descs: turn left, walk to the counter on the left
grab the spoon on the counter
put the spoon in the sink, wash the spoon, take the spoon
open the first drawer on the right, put the spoon in, close the drawer
anns.task_desc: wash the spoon in the sink, put the spoon in the drawer

high_descs: Turn left and left again to the counter.
Pick up the ladle from the counter.
Turn around and put the ladle in the sink.
Wash the ladle in the sink and pick it back up.
Turn around until you see the drawer on the left of the sink.
Put the ladle in the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Wash the ladle and put it away in the drawer.

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward to face the table in the center of the kitchen.
Pick up the ladle on the table in the center of the kitchen.
Turn around to face the sink.
Wash the ladle in the sink and then remove it.
Step to the right to face the drawer under the right end of the counter.
Place the ladle in the drawer on the right.
anns.task_desc: To wash a ladle as well as store it in a drawer on the right end of the counter.
